articles.description: Corey Kispert led a balanced attack with 14 points and No. 9 Gonzaga beat Loyola Marymount 76-46 on Thursday night to retain at least a share of first place in the West Coast Conference.
articles.headline: Williams leads No. 9 Gonzaga over Loyola Marymount 76-46

articles.description: Josh Ajayi had 26 points to go with 14 rebounds to help South Alabama continue its domination of Appalachian State with a 77-66 win over the Mountaineers in Sun Belt Conference action on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Ajayi has 26 points, 14 boards as South Alabama wins 77-66

articles.description: Paul Thomas took an inbounds pass in the wing and drove for the hoop, beating his defender with a spin move to hit a short jumper with two seconds left and UTEP edged Charlotte 87-86 Thursday night in a battle of two teams eager for a win.
articles.headline: Thomas scores winner as UTEP clips Charlotte 87-86

videos.description: JoJo Cooper cuts through the Seton Hall defense and scores a high-arcing layup off glass for the Seahawks.
videos.headline: Wagner's Cooper goes glass for bucket

videos.description: Desi Rodriguez gets the lob pass from Sandro Mamukelashvili and scores the bucket, while being fouled to extend the lead for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Rodriguez muscles  in and scores layup and-1

videos.description: Michael Nzei comes over on help side defense and blocks the shot attempt into the stands.
videos.headline: Nzei comes over for nasty block

videos.description: Myles Powell puts the ball on the deck and makes a right-handed layup off glass to extend the lead for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Powell scores fast break layup and-1

videos.description: Devin Liggeons scores an easy layup after cutting to the basket and taking the dish from AJ Sumby.
videos.headline: Wagner's Liggeons makes layup off the backdoor cut

videos.description: Angel Delagado post up and scores off the drop step move for an easy two points.
videos.headline: Delgado powers in for the basket

videos.description: Desi Rodriguez misses the fast-break dunk attempt and lands awkwardly on his left side, forcing him to leave the game with an apparent injury.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Rodriguez leaves game with injury

videos.description: Myles Powell scores an easy layup in transition to give the Pirates its largest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Powell rolls in an easy layup

videos.description: Myles Powell electrifies the crowd with a nasty right-handed slam in transition.
videos.headline: Powell throws down the funky dunk

videos.description: Seton Hall's Khadeen Carrington rejects Wagner's JoJo Cooper's layup attempt in transition to the delight of the Seton Hall faithful.
videos.headline: Carrington rejects Cooper  on the fast break
